# Fixing the Compilation Errors

You have 3 errors to fix. Let me address each one:

## 1. Fix `AppDatabase.kt` - Missing return statement

The `synchronized` block returns `Unit` because `INSTANCE = instance` is an assignment. Add `instance` on the next line:

```kotlin
fun getDatabase(context: Context): AppDatabase {
    return INSTANCE ?: synchronized(this) {
        val instance = Room.databaseBuilder(
            context.applicationContext,
            AppDatabase::class.java,
            "grocery_database"
        )
        .addMigrations(MIGRATION_1_2)
        .build()
        INSTANCE = instance
        instance  // ← ADD THIS LINE
    }
}
```

